snippet.description:
http://superfamicom.org/blog/
As requested by lytron87.
This is an advertisement for "BS Ihatovo Monogatari" that played at the end of BS Tantei Club episodes. This was recorded on the BS Tantei Club Zenpen video that was deleted off NND, so I segmented out the ad to show here.
